==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Zincoid
<hw>Zinc"oid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Zinc</ets> +
<ets>-oid</ets>.]</ety> <def>Pertaining to, or resembling, zinc; -- said
of the electricity of the zincous plate in connection with a copper
plate in a voltaic circle; also, designating the positive pole.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

